"Connected — usage is coming through." = "已连接——正在获取用量。";
"Codex is installed but signed out. Run `codex login`, then run Codex once." = "Codex 已安装但未登录。运行 `codex login`，然后运行一次 Codex。";
"Codex is signed in but hasn't written a session log yet. Run Codex once." = "Codex 已登录但尚未写入会话日志。请运行一次 Codex。";
"Install Claude Code and run it once. Token Meter needs no CLI on your PATH — it only reads the session logs." = "安装 Claude Code 并运行一次。Token Meter 不需要 CLI 在你的 PATH 中——它只读取会话日志。";
"Claude Code's sign-in has expired. Open Claude Code, run /login to sign in again, then Re-check." = "Claude Code 的登录已过期。打开 Claude Code，运行 /login 重新登录，然后点击“重新检查”。";
"Claude Code is present but hasn't written a session log yet. Start a session, then Re-check." = "Claude Code 已存在但尚未写入会话日志。请开始一个会话，然后点击“重新检查”。";
"macOS is blocking access. Grant Token Meter access in System Settings > Privacy & Security, then Re-check." = "macOS 正在阻止访问。请在“系统设置 > 隐私与安全性”中授予 Token Meter 访问权限，然后点击“重新检查”。";
"Not connected yet. Follow the steps in Setup, then Re-check." = "尚未连接。请按“设置”中的步骤操作，然后点击“重新检查”。";
"Open Claude Code and run /login to refresh the sign-in, then re-check" = "打开 Claude Code 并运行 /login 刷新登录，然后重新检查";
"Claude Code's sign-in has expired, so plan usage can't be loaded. Open Claude Code and run /login to sign in again, then re-check." = "Claude Code 的登录已过期，因此无法加载套餐用量。打开 Claude Code，运行 /login 重新登录，然后重新检查。";
"Sign in to Claude Code" = "登录 Claude Code";
"Allow Keychain access" = "允许访问钥匙串";
"Get Claude Code" = "获取 Claude Code";
"Token Meter asks first, then opens Terminal and runs `claude` — type /login there." = "先征求你的确认，然后打开终端并运行 `claude` — 在其中输入 /login。";
"Token Meter asks first, then macOS shows its own approval dialog. Choose Always Allow to stop the prompts." = "先征求你的确认，然后由 macOS 显示自己的授权对话框。选择“始终允许”即可不再反复询问。";
"Token Meter asks first, then opens the Claude Code download page in your browser." = "先征求你的确认，然后在浏览器中打开 Claude Code 下载页面。";
"Rather do it yourself? Manual steps" = "想自己操作？查看手动步骤";
"Manual steps…" = "手动步骤…";
"OK" = "好";
"Let macOS ask about the Claude Code sign-in?" = "让 macOS 询问 Claude Code 登录信息的访问权限？";
"Token Meter will read the “Claude Code-credentials” Keychain item once, right now. macOS shows its own approval dialog — choose Always Allow so it stops asking on every refresh. The token is only used to ask Anthropic for your plan usage, and is never stored, logged, or put in the widget." = "Token Meter 现在只会读取一次“Claude Code-credentials”钥匙串项目。macOS 会显示自己的授权对话框——选择“始终允许”，之后每次刷新就不会再询问。该令牌仅用于向 Anthropic 查询你的套餐用量，不会被保存、记录，也不会写入小组件。";
"Keychain access granted" = "已允许访问钥匙串";
"Token Meter can read the Claude Code sign-in and will show your plan usage from the next refresh." = "Token Meter 现在可以读取 Claude Code 的登录信息，将从下次刷新开始显示套餐用量。";
"Keychain access granted. Claude plan usage will appear on the next refresh." = "已允许访问钥匙串。Claude 套餐用量将在下次刷新时显示。";
"macOS denied access to the Claude Code sign-in" = "macOS 拒绝了对 Claude Code 登录信息的访问";
"Open Keychain Access, search for “Claude Code-credentials”, open it, and allow Token Meter under Access Control. Then try again. You can also turn the Claude usage check off in Settings and keep using local token counts." = "打开“钥匙串访问”，搜索并打开“Claude Code-credentials”，在“访问控制”中允许 Token Meter，然后重试。你也可以在设置中关闭 Claude 用量查询，只使用本地令牌统计。";
"Open Keychain Access" = "打开钥匙串访问";
"macOS denied access to the Claude Code sign-in. Allow Token Meter in Keychain Access, then try again." = "macOS 拒绝了对 Claude Code 登录信息的访问。请在“钥匙串访问”中允许 Token Meter，然后重试。";
"Your Claude Code sign-in has expired — open Terminal to sign in again?" = "你的 Claude Code 登录已过期——打开终端重新登录？";
"Open Terminal and sign in to Claude Code?" = "打开终端并登录 Claude Code？";
"Token Meter will open Terminal and run `claude`. Type /login once it starts and finish the sign-in in your browser. Token Meter never sees or types your password, and cannot complete the sign-in for you." = "Token Meter 将打开终端并运行 `claude`。启动后输入 /login，并在浏览器中完成登录。Token Meter 不会看到或输入你的密码，也无法代你完成登录。";
"Open Terminal" = "打开终端";
"Terminal is open. Type /login in Claude Code, then re-check here." = "终端已打开。请在 Claude Code 中输入 /login，然后回到这里重新检查。";
"Could not open Terminal. Follow the manual steps instead." = "无法打开终端，请改用手动步骤。";
"Open the Claude Code download page?" = "打开 Claude Code 下载页面？";
"Claude Code was not found on this Mac. Token Meter will open claude.com/claude-code in your browser. Install Claude Code, run it once and sign in, then come back and re-check." = "在这台 Mac 上未找到 Claude Code。Token Meter 将在浏览器中打开 claude.com/claude-code。请安装 Claude Code，运行一次并登录，然后回来重新检查。";
"Open browser" = "打开浏览器";
"The download page is open in your browser. Install Claude Code, sign in once, then re-check here." = "已在浏览器中打开下载页面。请安装 Claude Code 并登录一次，然后回到这里重新检查。";
"The manual steps are open in your browser." = "已在浏览器中打开手动步骤。";
"Could not read the Claude Code sign-in (Keychain error %d)." = "无法读取 Claude Code 登录信息（钥匙串错误 %d）。";
"Number format" = "数字格式";
"Token number format" = "令牌数字格式";
